        ],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "If you've ever stared at a dashboard wondering *why* users drop off before completing signup, you already know the gap most analytics tools leave behind. ",
            "marks": []
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Amplitude",
            "marks": [
              "l0"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " fills that gap. It's a ",
            "marks": []
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "product analytics platform",
            "marks": [
              "l1"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " built to show you exactly what users do inside your product, where they get stuck, and what to build next—all backed by real behavioral data.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "I've used a lot of analytics tools over the years. Amplitude consistently wins because it focuses on *product* behavior, not just pageviews. The free Starter plan is generous enough to run a real business on, and the AI-powered workflows save hours of manual digging.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "This tutorial walks you through setting up Amplitude from zero to actionable insights. No fluff—just the steps that matter.",
            "marks": []
