            "_type": "span",
            "text": "amplitude.com",
            "marks": [
              "l2"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " and click \"Start for free.\" The Starter plan gives you 10,000 monthly tracked users (MTUs), up to 2 million events, session replay, unlimited feature flags, and web experimentation—all without paying a cent.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "During signup, you'll name your first project. Pick something that reflects your product (e.g., \"MySaaS - Production\"). You can always add more projects later.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Once you're in, Amplitude drops you into a clean dashboard. No clutter, no overwhelming menus. You'll see prompts to install tracking, which brings us to the next step.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [
