        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Build these cohorts with Amplitude's visual query builder. No SQL required. Then use them everywhere: in funnels, retention charts, segmentation, and even as audiences you sync to marketing tools like Braze or HubSpot.",
